def compute_ratio(x):
    total = len(x)  # Grup içindeki toplam değer sayısı
    specific_value_count = sum(x == 0)  # Belirli bir değerin grup içinde kaç kez görüldüğü
    return 1-(specific_value_count / total)

df_day['duration'] = df_trio["Discount_ratio_price"].groupby(pd.Grouper(freq="1440min")).apply(compute_ratio)

df_day["monthday"]=df_day["date"].apply(lambda x: x.day)
df_day["month"]=df_day["date"].apply(lambda x: x.month)
df_day["year"]=df_day["date"].apply(lambda x: x.year)
df_day["quarter"]=df_day["date"].apply(lambda x: 1+((x.month-1)//3))

def checker(df,dt):
    flag=1
    if len(dt)>3:
        flag=int(.25*len(dt))+1
    for i in dt:
        if df.loc[i]["duration"]==0:
            flag-=1
        if flag==0:
            return False
    return True
def discounter(df,dt,discount):
    for i in dt:
        df.loc[i, "discount"] = discount
df_day["discount"]=0
for key,value in discounts_dict.items():
    for dt in value:
        try:
            if checker(df_day,dt):
                discounter(df_day,dt,key)
        except KeyError:
            print(dt," bu tarihler yok")

dayRate=[]
totalDay=[]
streak=0
for i in range(len(df_day)):
    if streak>0:
        streak-=1
        continue
    if df_day.iloc[i]["isDis"]:
        streak+=1
        while df_day.iloc[i+streak]["isDis"]:
            streak+=1
        for j in range(1,streak+1):
            dayRate.append(j)
            totalDay.append(streak)
        streak-=1
    else:
        dayRate.append(0)
        totalDay.append(0)
df_day["DiscountDay"]=dayRate
df_day["TotalDiscountDay"]=totalDay
